Document: MeshLibrary
Path: godot/classes/class_meshlibrary.rst
Summary: Describes the MeshLibrary resource, which stores meshes, collision, and navigation shapes for use in GridMap.

A library of meshes. Contains a list of Mesh resources, each with a name and ID. Each item can also include collision and navigation shapes. This resource is used in GridMap.
